    "MethodologyAn academic performance prediction model (APP-TGN) based on a revised low-high filtering temporal graph network is proposed in this section.",
    "The proposed APP-TGN considers temporal information and interaction behaviors to enhance the performance of model predictions.",
    "Furthermore, a data bias deduction module with global sampling techniques is developed to mitigate the problem of false correlations in deep learningbased models.",
